guides.title: Introduction to AAJOGOSS
guides.text: AAJOGOSS is a mobile application designed specifically for people who love playing word games. The app is easy to use and provides a great way to exercise the brain while having fun. AAJOGOSS works by challenging users to create as many words as possible from a set of letters, with different levels of difficulty suitable for players of all skill levels.

guides.title: How to Play AAJOGOSS
guides.text: To play AAJOGOSS, users need to start by choosing a level of difficulty that suits their skill level. The game will then show a series of letters, and the goal is to create as many words as possible using these letters. Points are awarded for each correct answer, and players can earn bonuses for longer words or for creating words that use all of the letters given.
